#### RFP Details

- The Government of Canada invites eligible suppliers to participate in the Request for Pre-qualifications (RFP) for the High-Frequency Rail (HFR) project.
- Suppliers who are interested in participating in the HFR project are requested to submit expressions of interest and qualifications during the RFQ stage.
- The project entails the development of an approximately 1,000-kilometer intercity passenger rail network with electrified tracks between major urban areas, including Toronto, Ottawa, Montreal, and Quebec City.
- Following the conclusion of a competitive procurement process with RFQ and RFP stages, Canada will engage a Private Developer Partner for project development and optimization.
- The notice officially closed on the tender finishing date of February 17, 2023, at 14:00:00 and has been officially cancelled.
